# Loan Approval Prediction Web App

This project presents a machine learning solution for automating loan approval decisions using a Random Forest model trained on 10,000 HELOC applications.

## 🔍 Features

- Data preprocessing, feature engineering, and hyperparameter tuning (GridSearchCV)
- Streamlit web app for real-time loan approval prediction
- SHAP-based explanation for model transparency
- Supports business decision-making with interpretable visual outputs

## 🚀 Live Demo

[Click here to try the app](https://harrison5668-streamlit-heloc-app-mlstreamlit-djgx0u.streamlit.app/)

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Python, pandas, scikit-learn, Streamlit, SHAP
- Jupyter Notebook
- Matplotlib & Seaborn (for visualization)

## 📁 Repository Contents

- `mlproject.ipynb`: Model training and evaluation
- `mlstreamlit.py`: Streamlit app code
- `shap_summary_plot.png`: SHAP visualization
- `requirements.txt`: Python package dependencies

